file.content:
openapi: 3.1.0
info:
    title: index
    version: '1.0'
servers:
    - url: 'http://localhost:3000'
tags:
    -
        name: unit-test
paths:
    /unit-test/v1/schema:
        get:
            tags:
                - unit-test
            operationId: GetSchema
            deprecated: false
            parameters:
                -   in: query
                    name: test_id
                    required: false
                    schema:
                        type: string
                -   in: query
                    name: unit_id
                    required: true
                    schema:
                        type: string
            responses:
                200:
                    content:
                        application/json:
                            schema:
                                $ref: '#/components/schemas/v1-required-response'
        post:
            tags:
                - unit-test
            operationId: PostSchema
            deprecated: false
            requestBody:
                required: true
                content:
                    application/json:
                        schema:
                            $ref: '#/components/schemas/v1-post-request-test'
            responses:
                200:
                    content:
                        application/json:
                            schema:
                                $ref: '#/components/schemas/v1-required-response'
        patch:
            tags:
                - unit-test
            operationId: PostSchema
            deprecated: false
            parameters:
                -   in: header
                    name: key
                    required: true
                    schema:
                        type: string
                -   in: query
                    name: unit_id
                    required: true
                    schema:
                        type: string
            requestBody:
                required: true
                content:
                    application/json:
                        schema:
                            $ref: '#/components/schemas/v1-patch-request-test'
            responses:
                200:
                    content:
                        application/json:
                            schema:
                                $ref: '#/components/schemas/v1-required-response'
    /unit-test/v1/schema/{test_id}:
        put:
            tags:
                - unit-test
            operationId: PutSchemaWithId
            deprecated: false
            parameters:
                -   in: header
                    name: x-api-key
                    required: true
                    schema:
                        type: string
            requestBody:
                required: true
                content:
                    application/json:
                        schema:
                            $ref: '#/components/schemas/v1-test-reference-model'
            responses:
                200:
                    content:
                        application/json:
                            schema:
                                $ref: '#/components/schemas/v1-required-response'
    /unit-test/v1/auto:
        post:
            tags:
                - unit-test
            operationId: PostAuto
            deprecated: false
            parameters:
                -   in: header
                    name: x-api-key
                    required: true
                    schema:
                        type: string
            requestBody:
                required: true
                content:
                    application/json:
                        schema:
                            $ref: '#/components/schemas/v1-test-reference-model'
            responses:
                200:
                    content:
                        application/json:
                            schema:
                                $ref: '#/components/schemas/v1-required-response'
    /unit-test/v1/auto/{id}:
        get:
            tags:
                - unit-test
            operationId: GetAuto
            deprecated: false
            parameters:
                -   in: header
                    name: x-api-key
                    required: true
                    schema:
                        type: string
            responses:
                200:
                    content:
                        application/json:
                            schema:
                                $ref: '#/components/schemas/v1-required-response'
        put:
            tags:
                - unit-test
            operationId: PutAuto
            deprecated: false
            parameters:
                -   in: header
                    name: x-api-key
                    required: true
                    schema:
                        type: string
            requestBody:
                required: true
                content:
                    application/json:
                        schema:
                            $ref: '#/components/schemas/v1-test-reference-model'
            responses:
                200:
                    content:
                        application/json:
                            schema:
                                $ref: '#/components/schemas/v1-required-response'
        delete:
            tags:
                - unit-test
            operationId: GetAuto
            deprecated: false
            parameters:
                -   in: header
                    name: x-api-key
                    required: true
                    schema:
                        type: string
                -   in: query
                    name: operation
                    required: true
                    schema:
                        type: string
            responses:
                200:
                    content:
                        application/json:
                            schema:
                                $ref: '#/components/schemas/v1-required-response'
components:
    schemas:
        v1-test-reference-model:
            type: object
            properties:
                test_id:
                    type: string
                object_key:
                    type: object
                    properties:
                        string_key:
                            type: string
                array_number:
                    type: array
                    items:
                        type: number
                array_objects:
                    type: array
                    items:
                        type: object
                        properties:
                            array_string_key:
                                type: string
                            array_number_key:
                                type: number
                fail_id:
                    type: string
        v1-test-request:
            allOf:
                - $ref: '#/components/schemas/v1-test-reference-model'
                - required:
                    - test_id
                    - object_key
                    - array_number
                    - array_objects
        v1-test-fail-request:
            allOf:
                - $ref: '#/components/schemas/v1-test-reference-model'
                - required:
                    - test_id
                    - object_key
                    - array_number
                    - array_objects
                    - fail_id
        v1-test-nullable-field:
            type: object
            required:
                - nullable_field
                - non_nullable_field
            properties:
                nullable_field:
                    type: string
                    nullable: true
                non_nullable_field:
                    type: string
        v1-required-response:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/v1-response-test-all-of'
        v1-response-test-all-of:
            allOf:
                - $ref: '#/components/schemas/v1-response-page'
                -
                    type: object
                    required:
                        - data
                    properties:
                        data:
                            $ref: '#/components/schemas/v1-response-result'
        v1-post-request-test:
            type: object
            required:
                - name
                - email
                - phone
                - active
            properties:
                name:
                    type: string
                email:
                    type: string
                phone:
                    type: number
                active:
                    type: boolean
        v1-patch-request-test:
            type: object
            required:
                - test_id
            properties:
                test_id:
                    type: string
                name:
                    type: string
                email:
                    type: string
                phone:
                    type: number
                active:
                    type: boolean
        v1-response-page:
            type: object
            properties:
                page_number:
                    type: number
            required:
                - page_number
        v1-response-result:
            type: object
            required:
                - id
            properties:
                id:
                    type: string
        v1-response-fail:
            type: object
            required:
                - id
            properties:
                id:
                    type: number
        v1-ddb-record:
            type: object
            required:
                - example_id
                - note
                - active
                - personal
                - transportation
            properties:
                example_id:
                    type: string
                note:
                    type: string
                active:
                    type: boolean
                personal:
                    type: object
                    properties:
                        gender:
                            type: string
                        last_name:
                            type: string
                        first_name:
                            type: string
                transportation:
                    type: array
        v1-ddb-record-fail:
            type: object
            required:
                - example_id
                - note
                - active
                - transportation
            properties:
                example_id:
                    type: string
                note:
                    type: string
                active:
                    type: number
                transportation:
                    type: array
